data.description: The Preston Plan built by My Home Communities.  The community is located 10 minutes from Atlanta Motor Speedway. This two-story  open floor plan, has an separate formal dining room, oversized island with granite counter tops that over look the spacious family room, 1/2 bath on first level, spacious open area on 2nd level, Oversized Primary Suite with trey ceilings, Super Shower, double vanities with granite counter tops and extra large spacious primary closet. The home also has a full masonary front, covered front and back porch with ceiling fan with a private back yard on a large lot. Quick Move-In! Ask about the 5.49 guaranteed rate plus $10,000 anyway you want with the use of the sellers approved lender and contracts binding by 01/31/2024
